title: Rutgers MBA Alumna Is President of Shaw University (Rutgers University)
text: ( Source : Rutgers University ) Photo courtesy of Tashni-Ann Dubroy Tashni-Ann Dubroy, Rutgers MBA '11, is the new president of Shaw University in Raleigh, North Carolina . No one has ever doubted Tashni-Ann Dubroy's ability to get things done.
